.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, dutch, german, polish
House: art-deco, townhouse, cottage, wooden
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, disaster, drama, romance
1. the person watching drama movies is on the far left##1
2. the person watching musical movies is between the person watching romance movies and the polish##2
3. the german is on the right of the townhouse house##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the cottage house##1
5. the german is on the right of the australian##1
6. the person watching romance movies is between the art-deco house and the person watching disaster movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | polish        | dutch   | australian | german |
| House         | cottage | art-deco | townhouse    | wooden |
| Movie-Genre     | drama       | musical     | romance       | disaster    |

