.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, lemonade, tea
There 4 different types of food: peas, watermelon, artichoke, mango
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, reggae, house, d&b
1. the fan of d&b is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking fanta##2
2. the fan of d&b is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of house##1
6. the fan of house is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
7. the fan of d&b is between the fan of house and the person eating peas##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | tea      | fanta       | lemonade   |
| Food      | peas   | watermelon  | mango | artichoke     |
| Music-Genre      | reggae     | d&b | house        | gospel |

