.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, ivory, light-blue, fuchsia
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, alhambra, ritmeester, dannemann
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rowing, soccer, swimming
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
5. the oliveros-smoker is between the dannemann-smoker and the person who's sport is soccer##2
6. the person who likes ivory is between the person who likes grey and the person who likes light-blue##2
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Color    | light-blue | ivory  | grey | fuchsia      |
| Cigar   | ritmeester  | dannemann  | oliveros | alhambra |
| Sport   | swimming | ice-hockey | rowing | soccer     |

