.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, colombian, indian, egyptian
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, march, june, may
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cycling, handball, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the indian is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the colombian is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in june##2
7. the egyptian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Nationality          | indian  | colombian    | egyptian | german  |
| Birthday   | june | may       | march        | january    |
| Sport         | cycling | badminton | volleyball  | handball |

