.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, country, gospel, electronic
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, fisherman, writer, scientist
4 different pets are kept: hamster, horse, lizard, rabbit
1. the scientist is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the fisherman is between the owner of the rabbit and the fan of country##2
3. the fan of gospel is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the scientist is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
6. the fan of gospel is on the left of the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Music-Genre         | electronic  | country | gospel | house |
| Job   | engineer  | scientist | fisherman   | writer         |
| Pet           | hamster | lizard  | horse   | rabbit      |

