.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, poppy, rose, orchid
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, photography, woodworking, writing
City: liverpool, hannover, marseilles, hamburg
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who growstulip##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who growspoppy##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Flower          | orchid  | tulip    | rose | poppy       |
| Hobby         | writing | photography | chess  | woodworking |
| City   | marseilles   | hamburg      | hannover  | liverpool     |

