.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, mauve, purple, aquamarine
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, dancing, gardening
House: modern, cottage, farmhouse, wooden
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes purple is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes mauve is between the person who likes red and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
4. the cottage house is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
6. the cottage house is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
7. the wooden house is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
8. the modern house is the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Color          | purple      | aquamarine | mauve | red |
| Hobby         | gardening   | collecting  | baking | dancing |
| House   | wooden | modern   | cottage | farmhouse |

