.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, garlic, raspberry, strawberry
City: prague, liverpool, san-francisco, new-york
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, may, april, march
1. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is the person eating garlic##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person eating strawberry##2
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person traveling to prague is the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the person traveling to new-york is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | strawberry  | raspberry | eggplant | garlic     |
| City   | prague | san-francisco   | new-york  | liverpool    |
| Birthday     | may        | march       | june      | april |

