.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, watermelon, raspberry, lime
House: cape-cod, victorian, wooden, modern
4 different pets are kept: bird, goat, pony, turtle
1. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person eating lime##1
2. the modern house is the person eating raspberry##1
3. the person eating watermelon is between the person eating raspberry and the victorian house##2
4. the wooden house is on the far left##1
5. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food   | lime | raspberry     | watermelon | blueberry       |
| House      | wooden  | modern | cape-cod  | victorian |
| Pet        | turtle  | goat      | pony        | bird      |

