There 4 different types of food: carrot, plum, cauliflower, garlic
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, pony, rabbit
1. the person who likes blue is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who likes blood-red and the person eating carrot##2
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
4. the person who likes azure is the owner of the pony##1
5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person eating plum##1
6. the person who likes blue is the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Color   | azure | blue  | blood-red       | aquamarine   |
| Food      | carrot     | cauliflower | plum | garlic |
| Pet        | pony        | rabbit | ferret     | hamster |

