.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, goldfish, ferret, fish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, fantasy, romance, time-travel
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, chaman, cain, aristoff
1. the person watching disaster movies is the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the cain-smoker is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the cain-smoker is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
5. the chaman-smoker is between the person watching romance movies and the owner of the ferret##2
6. the aristoff-smoker is on the far right##1
7. the chaman-smoker is the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Pet           | goldfish | fish | ferret    | rat   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance      | fantasy   | time-travel | disaster |
| Cigar     | ritmeester     | chaman       | cain        | aristoff    |

