.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, daisy, lily, sunflower
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, police-officer, project-manager, security-guard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, punk, r&b, techno
1. the person who growslily is the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of techno is the person who growssunflower##1
3. the person who growspoppy is the security-guard##1
4. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
5. the fan of punk is between the paramedic and the person who growspoppy##2
6. the project-manager is on the left of the fan of house##1
7. the fan of house is between the fan of techno and the fan of punk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Flower   | lily   | daisy           | poppy         | sunflower      |
| Job     | paramedic | project-manager | security-guard | police-officer |
| Music-Genre   | r&b     | punk         | house       | techno        |

