.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg, monopoly, canasta
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, freelancer, pilot, videographer
There are 4 different nationalities: german, indian, italian, mexican
1. the musician is the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person playing backgammon is between the person playing monopoly and the indian##2
3. the person playing monopoly is the freelancer##1
4. the person playing monopoly is between the pilot and the mexican##2
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
6. the german is between the italian and the videographer##2
7. the musician is the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Game      | mah-jongg | monopoly | backgammon   | canasta |
| Job   | musician  | freelancer    | pilot   | videographer     |
| Nationality   | mexican  | italian | german | indian   |

