.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, climbing, lacrosse, baseball
4 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, billiard, go
4 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, horse, mouse
1. the person playing billiard is the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the person playing go is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person playing billiard and the person playing snooker##2
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the owner of the mouse is between the person who's sport is climbing and the owner of the cat##2
7. the person playing go is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Sport      | lacrosse | swimming | climbing     | baseball   |
| Game   | snooker | go        | billiard  | mah-jongg  |
| Pet           | cat      | mouse         | hedgehog | horse |

