.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-19::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, d&b, rock, classical
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, apricot, ebony, blue
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, scooter, subway, taxi
1. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the fan of rock##1
2. the person who likes blue is the person driving the roller##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the subway is the fan of classical##1
5. the person who likes blood-red is the person driving the subway##1
6. the person driving the taxi is between the person who likes apricot and the person driving the subway##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Music-Genre         | electronic        | classical  | rock | d&b   |
| Color       | blue | blood-red | ebony    | apricot |
| Transport   | roller        | subway     | taxi       | scooter      |

