.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cabbage, strawberry, watermelon
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, aristoff, pall-mall, alhambra
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, january, march, september
1. the bongani-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
4. the person eating strawberry is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is the alhambra-smoker##1
6. the aristoff-smoker is between the person eating watermelon and the person who's birthday is in march##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | watermelon | cabbage | asparagus | strawberry |
| Cigar         | bongani       | aristoff     | pall-mall   | alhambra   |
| Birthday   | december | january | march | september |

 